## PROCs E SIMBOLICOS

```jcl
//*================================================================*
//* PROC: PAYPROC - Processamento de Folha                          *
//*================================================================*
//PAYPROC  PROC ENV='PROD',
//         SISTEMA='PAYROLL',
//         DTREF='&LYYMMDD',
//         MAXRC=0
//*
//*--------------------------------------------------------------*
//* STEP010 - SORT: Ordena transacoes por chave de funcionario    *
//*--------------------------------------------------------------*
//STEP010  EXEC PGM=SORT,REGION=256M
//SORTIN   DD DSN=&ENV..&SISTEMA..DATA.TRANSAC,DISP=SHR
//SORTOUT  DD DSN=&&SORTED,
//         DISP=(NEW,PASS),
//         SPACE=(CYL,(50,10),RLSE),
//         DCB=(RECFM=FB,LRECL=200,BLKSIZE=0)
//SYSIN    DD *
  SORT FIELDS=(1,10,CH,A)
  SUM FIELDS=NONE
/*
//SYSOUT   DD SYSOUT=*
//*
//*--------------------------------------------------------------*
//* STEP020 - COBOL: Calculo principal da folha                   *
//*--------------------------------------------------------------*
//STEP020  EXEC PGM=PGMPAY01,REGION=512M,
//         COND=(4,LT)
//STEPLIB  DD DSN=&ENV..&SISTEMA..LOAD.LOADLIB,DISP=SHR
//FUNCFILE DD DSN=&ENV..&SISTEMA..DATA.MASTER,DISP=SHR
//TRANFILE DD DSN=&&SORTED,DISP=(OLD,DELETE)
//OUTFILE  DD DSN=&ENV..&SISTEMA..DATA.RESULT(&DTREF),
//         DISP=(NEW,CATLG,DELETE),
//         SPACE=(CYL,(100,20),RLSE),
//         DCB=(RECFM=FB,LRECL=300,BLKSIZE=0)
//SYSOUT   DD SYSOUT=*
//SYSPRINT DD SYSOUT=*
//*
//         PEND
```

## TRATAMENTO DE CONDITION CODES

Prefira IF/THEN/ELSE/ENDIF (mais legivel que COND):

```jcl
//*--------------------------------------------------------------*
//* VERIFICACAO DE CONDITION CODES                                *
//*--------------------------------------------------------------*
//CHKSTEP IF (STEP020.RC > 4) THEN
//*
//*--------------------------------------------------------------*
//* STEP090 - ERRO: Notifica equipe e aborta processamento        *
//*--------------------------------------------------------------*
//STEP090  EXEC PGM=IKJEFT01
//SYSTSPRT DD SYSOUT=*
//SYSTSIN  DD *
  SEND 'PAYROLL - ERRO NO STEP020 - RC > 4' USER(OPER)
/*
//CHKSTEP ELSE
//*
//*--------------------------------------------------------------*
//* STEP030 - Geracao de relatorios (somente se STEP020 OK)       *
//*--------------------------------------------------------------*
//STEP030  EXEC PGM=PGMPAY02,REGION=256M
//STEPLIB  DD DSN=&ENV..&SISTEMA..LOAD.LOADLIB,DISP=SHR
//INFILE   DD DSN=&ENV..&SISTEMA..DATA.RESULT(&DTREF),DISP=SHR
//RPTFILE  DD SYSOUT=*
//*
//CHKSTEP ENDIF
```

## GDG (Generation Data Groups)

```jcl
//*--------------------------------------------------------------*
//* DEFINICAO DE GDG (executar uma vez via IDCAMS)                *
//*--------------------------------------------------------------*
//DEFGDG   EXEC PGM=IDCAMS
//SYSPRINT DD SYSOUT=*
//SYSIN    DD *
  DEFINE GDG -
    (NAME(PROD.PAYROLL.DATA.HISTORY) -
     LIMIT(30) -
     NOEMPTY -
     SCRATCH)
/*
//*
//* Referencia ao GDG no JCL:
//* Nova geracao:   DSN=PROD.PAYROLL.DATA.HISTORY(+1)
//* Geracao atual:  DSN=PROD.PAYROLL.DATA.HISTORY(0)
//* Geracao anterior: DSN=PROD.PAYROLL.DATA.HISTORY(-1)
```

## DFSORT / ICETOOL

```jcl
//*--------------------------------------------------------------*
//* STEP050 - ICETOOL: Relatorio de totais por departamento       *
//*--------------------------------------------------------------*
//STEP050  EXEC PGM=ICETOOL
//TOOLMSG  DD SYSOUT=*
//DFSMSG   DD SYSOUT=*
//INDD     DD DSN=&ENV..&SISTEMA..DATA.RESULT(0),DISP=SHR
//OUTDD    DD SYSOUT=*
//TOOLIN   DD *
  DISPLAY FROM(INDD) LIST(OUTDD) -
    TITLE('RELATORIO FOLHA POR DEPARTAMENTO') -
    DATE -
    PAGE -
    HEADER('DEPTO') ON(15,4,CH) -
    HEADER('TOTAL SALARIOS') ON(50,11,PD,2) -
    HEADER('QTD FUNCS') ON(1,10,CH,COUNT) -
    BREAK(15,4,CH)
/*
```

## BOAS PRATICAS

- TODA DD statement deve ter comentario explicando seu proposito
- Use `REGION=0M` no JOB card para nao limitar memoria
- Use `BLKSIZE=0` para deixar o sistema calcular o bloco otimo
- Use `RLSE` em SPACE para devolver espaco nao utilizado
- PROCs devem ter simbolicos com valores default para TODOS os parametros
- Use `&&` para datasets temporarios (passados entre steps)
- NUNCA hardcode datasets -- use simbolicos
- Prefira DISP=(NEW,CATLG,DELETE) para outputs criticos (delete on abend)
